{{collection}}

Welcome to the Wikibooks textbook on Physics, designed to contain everything you need to know for the OCR Physics B (Advancing Physics) specification[http://www.ocr.org.uk/download/kd/ocr_9654_kd_gce_spec.pdf]. All sorts of useful documents for this specification are available at http://www.ocr.org.uk/qualifications/type/gce/science/physics_b/index.html .

All units are assumed to be [[A-level_Physics/The_SI_System_of_Units|SI units]], unless stated otherwise. Diagrams can be enlarged by clicking on them.

Chapters are probably marked as 75% complete ({{stage short|75%}}) because they are complete, but may require some attention. Please look at these and check them!

