==Ingredients== *8oz Self Raising flour *2 tsp baking powder *8oz rolled oats *4oz sugar *6oz black treacle *8oz butter/margarine
==Procedure== # Put the butter or margarine, sugar and treacle into a saucepan and stir over a low heat until the fat and sugar have melted. # Add the porridge oats, flour and baking powder and blend thoroughly. # Press into two well greased 7" round sandwich tins. # Bake in the centre of a moderate oven at 180c or 350f or gas mark 4 for 20-25 minutes or until cooked through (test with a skewer). # Mark into slices whilst warm. # Allow to become almost cold in the tin before removing.

