== Copyrights ==
Hello, GireeshSharma, how are you? I saw the two pages you created. If you are planning to donate your books to Wikibooks, you should read [[WB:DONATE]]. That page has lots of information about book donations. Specifically, you must relicense your books under the [[GFDL]] license. I hope this is acceptable for you. --'''Whiteknight'''&nbsp;([[User:Whiteknight|Page]])&nbsp;([[User talk:Whiteknight|Talk]]) 05:07, 20 December 2007 (UTC)
